text: Robotboy is a British-French animated television series produced by Alphanim for Cartoon Network in the United Kingdom. ==Cast== * Laurence Bouvard as Robotboy, Robotgirl, Lola Mbola, Miu-Miu, Hester Turner, additional voices * Lorraine Pilkington as Tommy Turnbull, Debbie Turnbull, and Computer Teacher ==Episodes== List of Robotboy episodes ==References== Category:Cartoon Network series Category:English-language television programs Category:2005 American television series debuts Category:2008 American television series endings
